name: Veronica
description:
Veronica lives in a chaotic capital city. She sells fresh fruit in the downtown market close to the clock tower. Veronica is an agile, quick-witted, and a sharp-tongued. She’s usually smiling and quite lucky.

Veronica dreamed that one day she would travel to the southern port city. It must be a beautiful location.

Her flower is yellow Snapdragon. It has many meanings depending on its color. Yellow snaps mean smiles, happiness, and overall good luck.
